<h1 class="Btitle">
Xi Jinping, Kim Jong Un hold talks in Beijing 
</h1>
<div class="wzzy">
<i class="source"> Source: Xinhua</i>|<i class="time"> 2018-03-28 07:43:07</i>|<i class="editor">Editor:  Xiang Bo</i> 
</div>
